Description: Provides functions to clean disease signatures, compute reversal
    scores against Connectivity Map (CMap) profiles, and visualize and
    summarize candidate drug hits across datasets. Includes pipeline
    orchestration, command-line interface, and reproducible configuration
    management.
URL: https://github.com/enockniyonkuru/drug_repurposing/tree/main/CDRPipe
BugReports: https://github.com/enockniyonkuru/drug_repurposing/issues
